                the modern Job applications at one go.</p>
            <a href="/jobs" class="btn btn-large btn-secondary font-weight-bold">View Jobs</a>
        </main>
    </div>
    <footer class=" text-center text-white-50">
        <p>&copy; Jobify 2021</p>
